<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بيع الْأَعْيَان الغائبة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الْمَذْهَب:</span> بَاطِل فِي الْمَنْصُور فِي الْخلاف.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">عِنْدهم:</span> صَحِيح وَخيَار الرُّؤْيَة ثَابت.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَنْقُول:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
